For SUSE install the following packages:

  emacs
  cvs
  gcc
  gcc-c++
  xorg-x11-devel
  ImageMagick-devel
  db-devel
  xpdf
  make
  libpng-devel

DrScheme requires the following:
  xorg-x11-Mesa-devel
  openssl-devel
  readline-devel
  ncurses-devel
  termcap  (and ln -s libtermcap.so.2 libtermcap.so)
